The '''''Court Gazette''''' was a tabloid newspaper tasked with covering the goings-on of [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] court during the height of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. [[Drost Elegin]] was often featured in the paper due to his propensity for rumormongering.

